00:18:37,011 --> 00:18:39,261
which is exactly
what that editorial said.

492
00:18:39,263 --> 00:18:40,562
I remember because I thought,

493
00:18:40,598 --> 00:18:42,982
"What person under 80
uses that phrase?"

