any dangers to it.

528
00:20:09,015 --> 00:20:10,597
Unless, of course,
for some reason

529
00:20:10,649 --> 00:20:13,233
these allegations against him
are dropped.

530
00:20:14,603 --> 00:20:16,770
Anita Gibbs called you,
didn't she?

531
00:20:16,772 --> 00:20:18,439
I have no idea
what you're talking about.

532
00:20:18,441 --> 00:20:19,823
I'm simply giving you
the courtesy

533
00:20:19,859 --> 00:20:21,579
of letting you know
that if I have to choose

534
00:20:21,610 --> 00:20:25,612
between your future
and this university's,

535
00:20:25,614 --> 00:20:27,364
I'm not choosing you.

536
00:20:27,416 --> 00:20:29,833
Well, then, please,
tell Ms. Gibbs

