00:20:29,869 --> 00:20:32,703
thank you for the courtesy.

538
00:20:40,963 --> 00:20:42,429
Scottie, what are you
doing here?

539
00:20:42,465 --> 00:20:44,214
I can't believe
you sent him to me.

540
00:20:44,266 --> 00:20:45,766
