00:24:24,770 --> 00:24:27,821
I tried to get Sheila to make
them unafraid, but I couldn't.

626
00:24:27,856 --> 00:24:30,691
That's all right.

627
00:24:30,693 --> 00:24:32,373
It's all right, Louis.
It's not your fault.

628
00:24:32,411 --> 00:24:34,945
<i>♪
♪</i>

