00:26:13,172 --> 00:26:16,590
I get it. You want to talk
about making a deal.

659
00:26:16,642 --> 00:26:18,892
I don't know
what I wanna do.

660
00:26:20,846 --> 00:26:24,231
I just--

661
00:26:24,266 --> 00:26:26,399
She said that she could
get you into Columbia,

662
00:26:26,435 --> 00:26:27,400
and you're right.

663
00:26:27,436 --> 00:26:28,768
It got into my head.

664
00:26:28,821 --> 00:26:30,020
Rachel, we've been
over this.

