694
00:27:42,060 --> 00:27:43,843
and the only problem is,
there's no record of me

695
00:27:43,896 --> 00:27:45,262
ever having
being accused of that.

696
00:27:45,264 --> 00:27:47,898
- The guy you saw in court.
