too good for my own hometown.

725
00:28:55,834 --> 00:28:57,500
Well, it wasn't true.

726
00:28:57,502 --> 00:28:59,169
But I knew
the real test for me

727
00:28:59,221 --> 00:29:00,804
wasn't making it
in my own hometown.

728
00:29:00,839 --> 00:29:02,339
It was making it
in the toughest city

729
00:29:02,391 --> 00:29:04,224
in the world, and as far
as I'm concerned,

730
00:29:04,259 --> 00:29:08,511
I haven't done that yet.

